{"tid":1530482,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國Adult Swim x Production I.G改編] 伊藤潤二《漩渦》動畫版Teaser","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:24:28.000Z","uid":8150,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"002e60083c385ecd7105ed2235b312e9ee51662d","tid":1530482,"uid":8150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2019/08/uzumaki-adult-swim-trailer-1202170158/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fuzumaki-adult-swim-trailer-1202170158%2F&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=466bdb64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2019/08/uzumaki-adult-swim-trailer-1202170158/</a><br />\n<br />\n由伊藤潤二創作、曾改編真人電影版與遊戲的長篇漫畫《漩渦》，美國卡通電視頻道Adult Swim旗下的Toonami宣布將與Production I.G USA合作製作《漩渦》迷你動畫系列，共全4話，將於2020年在Toonami上播出。<br />\n&lt;STAFF&gt;<br />\n監督：長濱博史《蟲師》<br />\n音樂：Colin Stetson《Hereditary》<br />\n製作公司：Production I.G<br />\n<br />\n《漩渦》講述了一個虛構的城市-黑渦鎮，受到涉及螺旋的超自然詛咒的困擾，該鎮的居民接連不斷地受到與漩渦有關的詛咒以及怪事發生，主角五島桐繪目睹男友父親遭受漩渦詛咒後，身邊的家人、同學、朋友陸續產生了巨變，漩渦的詛咒不會停止，它將使所有人逐漸走向崩潰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDEQyK5ZH-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDEQyK5ZH-E&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7ea34218\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDEQyK5ZH-E</a>"},{"pid":"24543c46612da5abf939176ee09ec23298de3c2f","tid":1530482,"uid":15050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"明明漫畫冇乜嘢，但係睇條片啲嘢可以有少少反胃"},{"pid":"1e71f191b37bc313818dc828bcf3551adf3f6a78","tid":1530482,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"老老實實....啲蝸牛人係咪真係咁好味??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee50ea9b4abfd70894d68881eea070f9